Running the code with Docker:

1) chose a place to hold the data (~20GB), called DATA here

2) build the docker container;  in this directory, run the following:

  docker build -f docker/blanca.docker -t blanca . 

3) run and mount DATA (data will be in /data in the container):

  docker run -it -v DATA:/data blanca:latest /bin/bash

4) in the container, run tests

 usage analysis:

 a) cd usage_analysis

 b) bash run.sh /data

 linked stackoverflowposts:

 a) cd stackLinkedPosts

 b) bash run.sh /data